column5: Let's hear some reports? Hopefully some of you have internet...4 days to go!!!! Can't wait
Fishing on Lac seul has been good but a lot of male walleyes. Hope the females turn on before the end of the week. Water down 2 feet. The spawn was a week and half ago.
lac des milles lac in thunder bay was excellent. some lakes were slow. overall it seemed good.
Jabs: What part of Lac Seul were you on? Surprised to hear water level is down 2 feet ? (down from "normal" or last year or ??)
